text_cleaned:
Mailmap updates for the NumPy 2.5.0 release.

Hi All,

The NumPy 2.5.x branch and first release is coming soon. We prefer actual names when listing the contributors, so it would help if the following folks could respond to this issue with a preferred name and email address in order that they can be properly credited. The email is needed for the .mailmap file. so will become part to the project history. TIA.

@neofelis2X (Neofelis)
@agp19d
@false200 (Div)
@mdrdope
@skyvanguard
@bonpyt

