text:
CI: use IBM self-hosted runner for native s390x tests

s390x runners are also available at https://github.com/IBM/actionspz. We would like to use them as well to get rid of cross-compiling and running tests under qemu for s390x too. I could raise a PR to incorporate the required workflow adjustments when s390x runners are added.

@mkumatag @rgommers

